        { "@type": "Question", "name": "What is GPTZero?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "GPTZero is an AI content detector founded in 2023 by Edward Tian. It analyzes text for signs of AI generation (low perplexity, low burstiness) and outputs a probability score that the content was written by a human or by an AI model like ChatGPT, Claude, or Gemini." }},
