        <h2 id="verdict">Is GPTZero worth it in 2026? Final verdict</h2>
        <p><strong>For educators: yes, absolutely.</strong> Classroom Mode (Origin) is the most useful authorship-verification feature on the market. Premium ($15/mo) covers most teacher workloads. The free tier handles occasional checks.</p>

        <p><strong>For publishers and HR: yes, with realistic expectations.</strong> The detector catches obvious AI but misses humanized content. Treat it as one signal, not a judgment.</p>

        <p><strong>For SEO professionals and content marketers: no.</strong> Google has explicitly said it doesn't penalize AI content. You are paying $15–$25/mo to solve a problem you don't have. Invest the same budget in research, writing quality, or done-for-you publishing instead.</p>

